room_title: Escape room "Asylum 2.0" by Twisted Key Escape Room in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 201 NE Wilshire Blvd Suite D Burleson, TX 76028
room_description: You are locked in the padded room of an asylum.  The doctors are on the way to retrieve their next patient for their twisted experiments.  Edgar Boyle is the only known patient to have ever escaped.  He has left a trail of clues for you must figure out how he did it before the doctors get back.  Do you have what it takes?  Are you up for the task?  Do you think you are twisted enough to escape the Asylum?
